  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/2078a0604659d8d5bb69522e80bf2626.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=121 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/4ef5a47f67b7dc76a854d85ed048e44c.poster.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/4ef5a47f67b7dc76a854d85ed048e44c.webm?t=1766782934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>Parse-O-Rhythm</strong>, you play as an AI with only one goal: <strong><i>Slash the errors out of files!</i></strong> Utilize nothing but the mouse and two buttons to slice and dice your way through positive and negative errors that permeate the files you go through.<br><br>You'll start out with easy jobs, but don't be fooled - Parse-O-Rhythm offers a wide variety of challenge to AIs that dare to take on its jobs. Some files will be no problem to beat, and others will feel like a tooth-and-nail battle to move onto the next job.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/04fb70703a37bcafaa42ac0fbaee5bf4.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=127 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/11cfd01a206b03e81b112e28e21ccbdd.poster.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/11cfd01a206b03e81b112e28e21ccbdd.webm?t=1766782934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>25 different levels across 7 albums</strong>, each with a different artist behind them and varying levels of difficulty.<br></li><li> <strong>Robust accessibility settings</strong> that allow you to control flash brightness, background contrast, screen shake and many other factors.<br></li><li> <strong>A calibration system</strong> to ensure you can enjoy the game even if you have audio delay.<br></li><li> <strong>Character customization</strong> that allows you to customize your player, its weapon, and whatever color, or lack thereof, you choose.<br></li><li> <strong>Banger electronic music</strong> <i>(allegedly)</i> from a variety of in-studio artists and licensed music from internet composers.<br></li><li> <strong>Dazzling visual effects</strong> to accompany slashing, changes in music energy and, yes, missing errors, too.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/80318b3c6c64cf43dffb5b2784d94e94.poster.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/80318b3c6c64cf43dffb5b2784d94e94.webm?t=1766782934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parse-O-Rhythm Demo</h2>Not entirely sure about the game yet? Feel free to try the demo, which includes:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>4 levels</strong> contained within the first album in the game.<br></li><li> <strong>Accessibility settings and calibration</strong> equal to the full version.<br></li><li> <strong>No custom keybindings</strong> or <strong>character customization</strong>.</li></ul><br>This game's development is very community driven, so if you have any feedback, ideas or more, consider joining the discord!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/2078a0604659d8d5bb69522e80bf2626.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=121 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/4ef5a47f67b7dc76a854d85ed048e44c.poster.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/4ef5a47f67b7dc76a854d85ed048e44c.webm?t=1766782934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>Parse-O-Rhythm</strong>, you play as an AI with only one goal: <strong><i>Slash the errors out of files!</i></strong> Utilize nothing but the mouse and two buttons to slice and dice your way through positive and negative errors that permeate the files you go through.<br><br>You'll start out with easy jobs, but don't be fooled - Parse-O-Rhythm offers a wide variety of challenge to AIs that dare to take on its jobs. Some files will be no problem to beat, and others will feel like a tooth-and-nail battle to move onto the next job.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/04fb70703a37bcafaa42ac0fbaee5bf4.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=127 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/11cfd01a206b03e81b112e28e21ccbdd.poster.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/11cfd01a206b03e81b112e28e21ccbdd.webm?t=1766782934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Core Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>25 different levels across 7 albums</strong>, each with a different artist behind them and varying levels of difficulty.<br></li><li> <strong>Robust accessibility settings</strong> that allow you to control flash brightness, background contrast, screen shake and many other factors.<br></li><li> <strong>A calibration system</strong> to ensure you can enjoy the game even if you have audio delay.<br></li><li> <strong>Character customization</strong> that allows you to customize your player, its weapon, and whatever color, or lack thereof, you choose.<br></li><li> <strong>Banger electronic music</strong> <i>(allegedly)</i> from a variety of in-studio artists and licensed music from internet composers.<br></li><li> <strong>Dazzling visual effects</strong> to accompany slashing, changes in music energy and, yes, missing errors, too.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/80318b3c6c64cf43dffb5b2784d94e94.poster.avif?t=1766782934\" width=600 height=536 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2988830/extras/80318b3c6c64cf43dffb5b2784d94e94.webm?t=1766782934\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Parse-O-Rhythm Demo</h2>Not entirely sure about the game yet? Feel free to try the demo, which includes:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> <strong>4 levels</strong> contained within the first album in the game.<br></li><li> <strong>Accessibility settings and calibration</strong> equal to the full version.<br></li><li> <strong>No custom keybindings</strong> or <strong>character customization</strong>.</li></ul><br>This game's development is very community driven, so if you have any feedback, ideas or more, consider joining the discord!",
